P\rightarrow T
\lnot P\lor T
(P\rightarrow\lnot T)\land(\lnot P\rightarrow\lnot T)
(\lnot P\lor\lnot T)\land(P\lor\lnot T)
(\lnot P\land P)\lor\lnot T
\lnot T
(P\rightarrow\lnot T)\land(\lnot P\rightarrow\lnot T)
